OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny rain or
OL,6,Fdrizzle soon easing, although could
OL,7,Freturn to the far south for a time,
OL,8,Fhowever a few clearer spells possible
OL,9,Fin the north. Otherwise, staying
OL,10,Fgenerally cloudy, with some hill fog
OL,11,Fpatches across western hills. Winds
OL,12,Feasing.
OL,13,
OL,14,CFriday:FCloud thinning and breaking,
OL,15,Fperhaps allowing the odd brighter
OL,16,Fspell, especially toward the north.
OL,17,FHowever, thicker cloud in the south
OL,18,Fcould give some patchy rain at times.
OL,19,FLight winds. Mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
