OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FCloudy
OL,6,FSaturday morning, gradually turning
OL,7,Fbrighter, an overnight frost possible.
OL,8,FWinds strengthening Sunday and Monday,
OL,9,Fwith some rain spreading east but also
OL,10,Fsome drier spells. Mild.
